331
00:26:12,920 --> 00:26:15,980
I just want to praise the Lord.

332
00:26:15,980 --> 00:26:16,920
You don't want crowns.

333
00:26:16,920 --> 00:26:19,279
That means you don't want to live for the Lord.

334
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,679
I want a crown.

335
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:24,360
You say, why do you want a crown?

336
00:26:24,360 --> 00:26:25,520
You want to wear that thing?

337
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:27,399
No, I love my hair.

338
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:29,779
I want to have that crown,

339
00:26:29,779 --> 00:26:32,080
because here's how I see heaven working out.

340
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,720
