hey, this is not mine.

345
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,119
This is yours.

346
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:53,080
I think we're gonna get them back,

347
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,760
and I think we're gonna give them back.

348
00:26:54,760 --> 00:26:56,320
I think we're gonna get them back,

349
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:57,720
and I think we're gonna give them back,

350
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,320
and if you want to miss out on that,

351
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:01,800
okay, you be fake humble.

352
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,520
I want to participate in that,

353
00:27:04,520 --> 00:27:06,520
and so bless God.

354
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:10,360
I am going to reach for that crown

355
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:12,399
until the day of his appearing.

356
00:27:12,399 --> 00:27:14,000
Here's second.

357
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,679
I'm going to obey,

358
00:27:15,679 --> 00:27:17,679
because I know that obedience

359
00:27:17,679 --> 00:27:20,660
is what must proceed being rewarded.

360
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,559
We've spoken much of Paul's effort

361
00:27:23,559 --> 00:27:25,880
and much of Paul's commitment,

362
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,520
but I want to be careful

363
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:30,959
that it is not about some superior human being

364
00:27:30,959 --> 00:27:32,700
making an extraordinary effort.

365
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:34,540
He did make an extraordinary effort,

366
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:36,619
but he's not a superior human being.

367
00:27:36,619 --> 00:27:39,059
Paul is no different than you and I.

368
00:27:39,059 --> 00:27:42,300
Paul did not have angel wings under his cloak.

369
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:45,260
Paul did not have any measure of the Spirit

370
00:27:45,260 --> 00:27:46,940
that we do not have access

371
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:48,420
to the measure of the Spirit.

372
00:27:49,300 --> 00:27:51,220
Paul had a calling of God

373
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:53,059
and a pathway of life,

374
00:27:53,059 --> 00:27:54,779
and I have a calling of God

375
00:27:54,779 --> 00:27:55,980
and pathway of life,

376
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,700
and you have a calling of God

