00:27:59,020 --> 00:28:00,500
All I'm saying is,

379
00:28:00,500 --> 00:28:02,500
is that when Paul was shipwrecked

380
00:28:03,339 --> 00:28:04,739
and when Paul was left for dead

381
00:28:04,739 --> 00:28:06,820
outside of Lystra and got back up,

382
00:28:06,820 --> 00:28:09,100
and when Paul and Silas sang

