00:29:13,660 --> 00:29:16,820
and I have one that is reserved for us,

405
00:29:18,099 --> 00:29:19,220
and God is watching.

406
00:29:20,859 --> 00:29:22,619
God is keeping track,

407
00:29:23,820 --> 00:29:27,700
