414
00:29:43,179 --> 00:29:44,900
and the Lord says to you,

415
00:29:44,900 --> 00:29:47,900
well done, thou good and faithful servant,

416
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:51,539
and you're not gonna stand before the Lord

417
00:29:51,539 --> 00:29:53,460
when he's got that crown of righteousness

418
00:29:53,460 --> 00:29:55,099
because you reached for it,

419
00:29:55,099 --> 00:29:58,099
because you lived focusing on his appearing.

420
00:29:58,099 --> 00:30:00,700
