00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:23,640
Go back to verse 8, henceforth there is laid up for me a crown of righteousness, which

439
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:30,760
the Lord, the righteous judge, shall give me at that day.

440
00:31:31,040 --> 00:31:36,160
Not today, at that day.

