00:32:03,040 --> 00:32:09,320
– to be at the Bema Seat is to have received Christ as your Savior.

447
00:32:09,320 --> 00:32:12,280
But please understand this.

448
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:19,280
The living of our life and whether it has been lived for Him will be a matter of judgment

449
00:32:20,280 --> 00:32:23,320
at the Bema Seat.

450
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:30,320
And all of a sudden that focus will seem very important.

451
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:33,080
What did I focus on?

452
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:35,680
What did I give myself to?

453
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,640
What occupied my mind?

454
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,400
What filled my heart?

455
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:43,280
Was there a little piece of the week, maybe a little piece of the day that was given to

