00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:49,960
the Lord, but primarily the focus of my life was chasing what the world had or thinking

457
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,940
that I had to do all that the world said?

458
00:32:52,940 --> 00:32:57,760
Or was I in my place doing what the Lord wanted me to do?

459
00:32:57,760 --> 00:33:00,580
Was that the focus of my life?

460
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:06,760
Because until the Lord appears, He has given us the command to occupy.

